ActCanadian Air Transport Security Authority Act
PrecisAppointment of CLÉMENT JOLY of Montréal, Quebec, to be a director of the board of directors of the Canadian Air Transport Security Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Pierre Beaudry, whose term has expired.
